text: Sydney Sweeney (born September 12, 1997) is an American actress. She is known for her roles in Netflix series Everything Sucks! (2018) as Emaline, Eden in the Hulu series The Handmaid's Tale (2018), Alice in the HBO miniseries Sharp Objects (2018) and Cassie Howard in the HBO teen drama series Euphoria. ==Awards and nominations== Award Year Category Work Result Ref.
